'''Volarik''' is an unseen character mentioned in the episode &quot;[[The Mountain and the Viper]]&quot;. He was the [[maester]] of [[Casterly Rock]].

sections.Biography:
Volarik was the [[maester]] serving [[House Lannister]] during the youth of [[Tyrion Lannister]].
===[[Season 4]]===
While reminiscing about [[Orson Lannister]], Tyrion mentions he visited Volarik's library looking for some reading that would help him understand Orson's mindset and his tendency to kill beetles. [[Jaime Lannister|Jaime]] has a quick reaction of disgust and remarks that Volarik had tried to touch (molest) him once.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Mountain and the Viper]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
